Project Title
GBDA302 Sidequest Week 9

Authors
Karen Cochrane and David Han

Members
Ebube Mbanefo

Description
This code adds a debug screen by pressing the "d" or "D" key which allows the player to toggle on and off the Moon Gravity feature. A temporary speed boost can also be activated by hitting the shift key and it lasts for approximately 5 seconds. I also changed the forward and backward keys to "a" and "s" respectively.

Learning Goals

- Implemented a debug feature for gameplay
- Implemented features (temporary speed boost) that can be used for potential game development.

Assets
N/A

GenAI
The code was written by Dr. Karen Cochrane but she used GenAI to write the comments.

Ebube Mbanefo used GenAI to help implement features and debug some errors in her code to complete the sidequest.
